The Media Board develops policies for and oversees the administration of ["The California Aggie"] and FM Radio Station ["KDVS"]. The Board approves media budgets, selects the media managers, and resolves grievances and reviews issues related to freedom of speech and press involving the media. The Board meets at least monthly throughout the academic year and may meet more frequently during the Winter and Spring Quarters. Membership includes:  2 Faculty/Staff and 5 Students, plus alternates and ex officio members. For further information, contact Student Affairs (530-752-8787). ([http://chancellor.ucdavis.edu/aac/descrip.htm source])

email: mediaboard@ucdavis.edu
